# Test REST API for Adjust Module
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/adjust
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here

### Test 1: Upload CSV file successfully
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="valid_adjust.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

KDTK,PRDCD,QTY_ADJ
T001,12345,10
T002,12345,5
T003,12345,-3
------WebKitFormBoundary--

