### Test 10: Get history by month
GET {{baseUrl}}/history?month=2025-11&limit=25&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 11: Get history by month with PIC and KDTK list
GET {{baseUrl}}/history?month=2025-11&pic=joko&kdtk[]=T001&kdtk[]=T002&status=SUCCESS&limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 12: Get filters (PIC/KDTK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/filters
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 13: Export history CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/export?month=2025-11&status=SUCCESS
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
